               <p>SIMPSON MORTON. I live at Messrs. Smith's, distillers. On the 25th of July I was opposite <placeName id="t18310908-170-crimeloc896">Little Eastcheap</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-170-crimeloc896" type="placeName" value="Little Eastcheap"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-170-crimeloc896" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-170-off894 t18310908-170-crimeloc896"></join> - I did not miss my handkerchief until somebody asked me if I had lost any thing; I found I had - the officer had the prisoner and my handkerchief in his hand.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-170-person1341">
                  RICHARD 
                  FULLER
               <interp inst="t18310908-170-person1341" type="surname" value="FULLER"></interp>
